          "slidecontent": "• Calibrate sensors and cameras before every flight or survey session\n• Use ground control points to anchor spatial data to real-world coordinates\n• Overlap image captures by at least 70% to reduce gaps in coverage\n• Check weather conditions, as wind and poor light distort readings\n• Validate outputs against known reference data before sharing results\n• Keep equipment serviced and firmware updated regularly"
